2%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EZayn%20Malik%20celebrated%20his%2032nd%20birthday%20with%20a%20'Last%20of%20Us'-themed%20cake%20resembling%20a%20fungal%20zombie.%20He%20thanked%20fans%20for%20their%20birthday%20wishes%20and%20support%20for%20his%20charitable%20causes.%20Malik%20praised%20the%20cake's%20creator%2C%20Elizabeth%20Rowe%2C%20for%20her%20artistic%20skills%2C%20calling%20it%20'the%20best%20cake'%20he'd%20had%20in%2032%20years.%20The%20post%20received%20positive%20reactions%20from%20fans%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20surprised%20that%20the%20singer%20was%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fzayn-malik-shows-off-his-last-of-us-themed-zombie-birthday-cake-sparks-excitement-among-fans-ahead-of-season-2-release%2Farticleshow%2F117190059.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20Z-Morh%20Tunnel%2C%20A%20Landmark%20Project%20In%20Jammu%20And%20Kashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20much-anticipated%20Z-Morh%20Tunnel%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Ganderbal%20district%20today.%20The%20project%20is%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20year-round%20connectivity%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Sonamarg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20has%20visited%20the%20site%20to%20review%20preparations%2C%20inspect%20the%20tunnel%2C%20and%20thank%20the%20engineers%20and%20workers%20for%20their%20dedication%20to%20the%20landmark%20project.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20PM%20Modi%20reacted%20and%20said%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-shares-pictures-of-new-z-morh-tunnel-in-j-k-pm-modi-reacts-7454145%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Beagerly%20awaiting%26quot%3B%20the%20tunnel%20inauguration%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20about%20the%20Z-Morh%20tunnel%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Z-Morh%20Tunnel%20derives%20its%20name%20from%20the%20Z-shaped%20stretch%20of%20road%20it%20replaces.%20%26quot%3BZ-Morh%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20Hindi%20for%20%26quot%3BZ-turn%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Z-Morh%20Tunnel%20connects%20Gagangir%20and%20Sonamarg%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Ganderbal%20district.%20It%20spans%206.5%20km%2C%20with%20an%20additional%206.05%20km%20of%20approach%20roads.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tunnel%20is%20situated%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%202%2C637%20metres%20(8%2C652%20feet)%20above%20sea%20level.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20provides%20all-weather%20access%20to%20Sonamarg%2C%20replacing%20the%20avalanche-prone%20Z-turn%20road.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tunnel%20is%20a%20two-lane%2C%20bi-directional%20road%20structure%20with%20a%20width%20of%2010%20metres.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20parallel%20escape%20tunnel%2C%207.5%20metres%20wide%2C%20is%20included%20for%20emergencies%20and%20dual%20use%20as%20a%20railway%20tunnel.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20designed%20to%20handle%20up%20to%201%2C000%20vehicles%20per%20hour%20at%20a%20maximum%20speed%20of%2080%20kmph.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tunnel%20has%20been%20built%20using%20the%20New%20Austrian%20Tunneling%20Method%20(NATM).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Z-Morh%20Tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20NH1%20Srinagar-Leh%20Highway.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20project%20was%20approved%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2024%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tunnel%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20ventilation%20system%20and%20has%20two%20portals%20-%20Western%20and%20Eastern.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Z-Morh%20Tunnel%20is%20one%20of%2031%20tunnels%20-%2020%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%2011%20in%20Ladakh%20-%20being%20constructed%20at%20a%20combined%20investment%20of%20Rs%202%2C680%20crore.%20Before%20the%20tunnel%2C%20the%20route%20was%20infamo