3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Prayagraj%2C%20UP%20%7C%20Laurene%20Powell%20Jobs%2C%20wife%20of%20the%20late%20Apple%20co-founder%20Steve%20Jobs%20reached%20Spiritual%20leader%20Swami%20Kailashanand%20Giri%20Ji%20Maharaj's%20Ashram%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy20yu7bDSU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fy20yu7bDSU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1878392194186498443%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2012%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Laurene%20will%20stay%20at%20the%20Niranjini%20Akhara%20camp%20till%20January%2015%2C%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20US%20to%20attend%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20arriving%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20she%20visited%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20in%20Varanasi%20on%20Saturday.%20She%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Swami%20Kailashanand%20Giri%20Maharaj%20of%20Niranjani%20Akhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20salwar%20suit%20and%20a%20dupatta%20on%20her%20head%2C%20Ms%20Laurene%20offered%20prayers%20from%20outside%20the%20main%20temple%20area.%20Swami%20Kailashanand%20explained%20that%20according%20to%20temple%20tradition%2C%20no%20one%20other%20than%20a%20Hindu%20can%20touch%20the%20Shivling%2C%20which%20is%20why%20she%20prayed%20from%20outside%20the%20sanctum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20an%20Acharya%2C%20and%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20uphold%20traditions%2C%20principles%2C%20and%20conduct%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20my%20daughter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20our%20family%20participated%20in%20the%20'Abhishek'%20and%20worshipped.%20She%20was%20given%20a%20prasad%20and%20a%20garland.%20However%2C%20the%20tradition%20is%20that%20anyone%20other%20than%20a%20Hindu%20cannot%20touch%20Kashi%20Vishwanath.%20If%20I%20do%20not%20maintain%20this%20tradition%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20broken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Kailashanand%20also%20spoke%20to%20ANI%20about%20her%20profound%20respect%20for%20Indian%20traditions%20and%20spirituality.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20very%20religious%20and%20spiritual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20wants%20to%20learn%20about%20our%20traditions.%20She%20respects%20me%20as%20a%20father%20and%20a%20Guru.%20Everyone%20can%20learn%20from%20her.%20Indian%20traditions%20are%20being%20accepted%20by%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20held%20at%20the%20confluence%20of%20the%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%2C%20and%20the%20mythical%20Saraswati%20rivers%2C%20witnessed%20a%20massive%20influx%20of%20devotees%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20nearly%2050%20lakh%20pilgrims%20taking%20a%20holy%20dip%20ahead%20of%20Paush%20Purnima%2C%20the%20first%20bathing%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremonial%20Amrit%20Snan%20(auspicious%20bath)%20is%20scheduled%20for%20January%2014%2C%20marking%20Makar%20Sankranti.%20All%20akharas%2C%20including%20Niranjini%20Akhara%2C%20will%20take%20their%20ordained%20dips%20in%20a%20sequence%2C%20with%20the%20Niranjini%20Akhara%20slated%20to%20bathe%20between%207%3A05%20am%20and%207%3A45%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736744400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fqffoca_laurene_625x300_13_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsteve-jobs-039-widow-laurene-powell-jobs-arrives-in-prayagraj-for-maha-kumbh-mela-7461265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Laurene%20Powell%20jobs%20will%20stay%20at%20the%20Niranjini%20Akhara%20camp%20till%20January%2015%20for%20Maha%20Kumbh%202025.%22%2C