0forces%20say%20is%20a%20North%20Korean%20soldier's%20diary.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20include%20a%20stick-figure%20sketch%20of%20using%20a%20comrade%20as%20%26quot%3Bbait%26quot%3B%20to%20shoot%20down%20a%20drone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOther%20entries%20include%20musings%20on%20class%20struggles%20and%20a%20confession%20for%20stealing%20undisclosed%20Russian%20items.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20a%20North%20Korean%20soldier's%20diary%20released%20by%20Ukraine%20show%20a%20glimpse%20at%20how%20Pyongyang's%20troops%20in%20Russia%20believed%20they%20could%20defend%20against%20drones%20and%20artillery%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20special%20forces%20have%20been%20releasing%20excerpts%20of%20the%20diary%20since%20Christmas%20week%2C%20saying%20the%20entries%20were%20written%20by%20a%20now-deceased%20North%20Korean%20private%20named%20Gyeong%20Hong%20Jong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20of%20these%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fukr_sof%2F1368%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20appeared%20to%20feature%20the%20young%20soldier%20confessing%20that%20he%20was%20stealing%20items%20from%20his%20Russian%20allies%20to%20sell.%20He%20did%20not%20specify%20what%20the%20stolen%20goods%20were%20but%20wrote%20that%20he%20had%20been%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20working%20in%20the%20barracks%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20no%20one%20was%20watching%20me%20and%20put%20the%20Russians'%20things%20in%20my%20pocket%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20diary%20excerpt%20said%2C%20per%20Ukraine's%20special%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20no%20longer%20trade%20in%20other%20people's%20things.%20I%20will%20heroically%20advance%20in%20the%20forefront%20and%20destroy%20the%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20soldier%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20entries%20released%20by%20Ukraine%20included%20praises%20of%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20and%20musings%20on%20class%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLonging%20for%20my%20homeland%2C%20having%20left%20the%20warm%20embrace%20of%20my%20dear%20father%20and%20mother%20here%20on%20Russian%20land.%20I%20celebrate%20the%20birthday%20of%20my%20closest%20comrade%20Song%20Ji%20Myong%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20entry%20read%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fdiary-of-a-dead-north-korean-soldier-reveals-grisly-battlefield-tactics-fafbede7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etranslation%20by%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20earliest%20entries%2C%20published%20by%20Ukraine%20on%20December%2026%2C%20featured%20a%20stick-figure%20drawing%20of%20what%20the%20soldier%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20eliminate%20a%20drone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20simple%20illustration%20showed%20a%20figure%20standing%20upright%20on%20open%20ground%20while%20another%20two%20stick%20figures%20fired%20at%20a%20quadcopter%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fjs%2Ftelegram-widget.js%3F22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20UAV%20is%20spotted%2C%20gather%20in%20groups%20of%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20diary%20read%2C%20per%20The%20Journal's%20translation.%20%26quot%3BOne%20person%20must%20act%20as%20bait%20to%20lure%20the%20drone%20while%20the%20other%20two%20take%20aim%20and%20neutralize%20it%20with%20precision%20shooting.%20The%20bait%20must%20maintain%20a%20distance%20of%20seven%20meters%20from%20the%20drone.%20The%20other%20two%20should%20prepare%20to%20shoot%20down%20the%20drone%20from%20a%20distance%20of%2010%20to%2012%20meters.%20When%20the%20bait%20stands%20still%2C%20the%20drone%20will%20stop%20and%20it%20can%20be%20shot%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20special%20forces%20said%20the%20North%20Korean%20soldier%20also%20wrote%20of%20how%20to%20avoid%20artillery%20strikes.%20An%20excerpt