.%20And%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20was%20okay%20because%20he%20was%20sitting%20down.%20I%20didn't%20realise%20we%20had%20him%20in%20handcuffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Luna%20told%20the%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20turning%20him%20over%20to%20LAPD%20because%20he%20was%20dressed%20like%20a%20fireman%2C%20and%20he%20was%20not.%20He%20just%20got%20caught%20burglarising%20a%20home.%20So%20those%20are%20issues%20that%20our%20front%20line%20deputies%20and%20police%20officers%20are%20dealing%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Mr%20Luna%2C%20about%2029%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20around%20the%20wildfires%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20area.%20One%20person%20was%20arrested%20Saturday%20night%20for%20violating%20a%20curfew%20order%20in%20the%20city%20while%20three%20others%20were%20arrested%20the%20night%20before%20in%20connection%20to%20an%20alleged%20burglary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20warned%20that%20the%206%20pm%20to%206%20am%20local%20time%20curfew%20remained%20in%20effect%20from%20Sunday%20night%20into%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20you're%20a%20public%20safety%20personnel%20or%20some%20other%20disaster%20worker%2C%20you%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20be%20at%20these%20locations.%20And%20if%20you%20are%20in%20those%20areas%2C%20you%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20arrest.%20Enforcing%20a%20curfew%20is%20an%20important%20tool%20to%20keep%20the%20burn%20areas%20and%20evacuated%20properties%20secure%2C%20keeping%20looters%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-caused-los-angeles-wildfires-elon-musk-donald-trump-blame-diversity-and-a-small-fish-7447562%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20What%20Caused%20Los%20Angeles%20Wildfires%3F%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20Blame%20Diversity%20And%20A%20Small%20Fish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDevastation%20by%20LA%20wildfire%3C%2Fst