7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bumrah%20Set%20To%20Lead%20In%20England%2C%20These%202%20Stars%20Captaincy%20Back-Ups%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20the%20frontrunner%20to%20replace%20Rohit%20Sharma%20as%20India's%20Test%20captain%20going%20forward%20but%20the%20peerless%20pacer%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20long-term%20option%20given%20his%20nagging%20fitness%20concerns%2C%20the%20latest%20being%20a%20back%20spasm%20which%20has%20rendered%20him%20doubtful%20for%20next%20month's%20Champions%20Trophy.%20Indian%20selectors%20are%20hopeful%20that%20he%20still%20might%20have%20some%20role%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20since%20it's%20a%20swelling%2C%20but%20when%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20bigger%20picture%20the%20question%20arises%20whether%20he%20can%20be%20deemed%20a%20permanent%20skipper%20in%20Tests%2C%20now%20that%20Rohit's%20days%20in%20whites%20look%20as%20good%20as%20over.%20If%20Bumrah%20is%20fit%20and%20ready%20to%20lead%20the%20Test%20side%20in%20England%2C%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20and%20his%20four%20colleagues%20need%20to%20have%20a%20strong%20name%20as%20vice-captain%20so%20that%20in%20case%20of%20an%20unforeseen%20scenario%2C%20the%20deputy%20is%20good%20enough%20to%20take%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20in%20Tests%2C%20only%20two%20names%20are%20in%20the%20reckoning%20--%20Rishabh%20Pant%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20--%20with%20the%20former%20looking%20the%20most%20suitable%20for%20that%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20understood%20that%20during%20BCCI's%20review%20meeting%20on%20Saturday%20with%20Agarkar%2C%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Rohit%2C%20Bumrah's%20issues%20with%20the%20lower%20back%20cropped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20review%20meeting%2C%20one%20can%20conclude%20that%20it%20is%20very%20unlikely%20Rohit%20will%20travel%20to%20England%20for%20the%20five%20Tests%2C%20and%20the%2031-year-old%20Bumrah%20will%20certainly%20lead%20the%20team%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20at%20Headingley%20if%20all%20goes%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pacer%20with%20443%20international%20scalps%20across%20formats%20in%20just%20203%20games%20led%20India%20at%20Perth%20and%20Sydney%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20and%20was%20the%20'player%20of%20the%20series'%20with%2032%20wickets%2C%20the%20highest%20by%20an%20Indian%20on%20foreign%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20back%20spasm%20in%20the%20final%20Test%20proved%20to%20be%20his%20undoing%20as%20he%20could%20not%20bowl%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20and%20is%20set%20to%20undergo%20rehabilitation%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20in%20Bengaluru%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20playing%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injury%20has%20raised%20questions%20whether%20Bumrah%20can%20remain%20fit%20for%20long%20periods%20given%20his%20workload%20as%20the%20pace%20spearhead%20in%20Tests%2C%20who%20is%20also%20required%20for%20ICC%20white-ball%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20guarantee%20that%20Bumrah%20won't%20have%20more%20breakdowns%20during%20the%20next%20WTC%20cycle%20from%20June%202025%20to%20June%202027%2C%20now%20that%20he%20is%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%2030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20selectors%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20have%20a%20Plan%20B%20ready%2C%20which%20is%20to%20have%20another%20equally%20strong%20captaincy%20candidate%2C%20who%20can%20be%20groomed%20as%20vice-captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20simple%20thing.%20You%20look%20at%20the%20data%20and%20find%20who%20is%20a%20sure-shot%20pick%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20Bumrah%20has%20played%2045%20Tests%20and%20Pant%20has%2043%20Tests.%20He%20(Pant)%20is%2027%20now%20and%20by%20the%20time%20he%20was%20only%2023%2C%20he%20had%20singlehandedly%20won%20India%20one%20of%20its%20greatest%20Tests%20at%20the%20Gabba.%20He%20is%20a%20match-winner%2C%20a%20good%20sounding%20board%20for%20bowlers%20and%20should%20be%20the%20vice-captain%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20national%20selector%20Devang%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20India%20keeper%20Deep%20Dasgupta%20agreed%20that%20Bumrah%20cannot%20be%20a%20long-term%20solution%20as%20Test%20captain%20given%20his%20bowling%20workloads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20just%20the%20marquee%20series%20(England%2C%20Australia)%20that%20we%20are%20talking%20about.%20In%20between%20Test%20matches%2C%20there%20will%20be%20ICC%20events%20where%20Bumrah's%20presence%20is%20a%20must.%20Like%20this%20year%2C%20it%20is%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%20next%20year%20it%20will%20be%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20He%20is%20managing%20it%20well%20by%20not%20playing%20bilaterals%20but%20nearer%20to%20events%2C%20he%20would%20need%20to.%20Then%20the%20bowling%20workload%20becomes%20paramount.%20Don't%20forget%20two%20months%20of%20IPL%2C%26quot%3B%20Dasgupta%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20even%20as%20Bumrah%20starts%20as%20the%20next%20Test%20captain%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20strong%20vice-captain%2C%20and%20yes%20Pant%20fits%20the%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20felt%20that%20Jaiswal%20should%20not%20be%20burdened%20with%20vice-captaincy%20considering%20that%20he%20will%20spearhead%20India's%20batting%20challenge%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20and%20there%20is%20still%20some%20time%20before%20the%20establishment%20can%20think%20of%20him%20in%20a%20leadership%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736738280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F4gq9e0i8_jasprit-bumrah_625x300_12_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fjasprit-bumrahs-injuries-a-concern-for-test-captaincy-bcci-to-keep-these-2-stars-ready-report-7457035%22