p%3EWhile%20Taylor's%20lifestyle%20in%20Malaysia%20is%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20similar%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20one%20he%20had%20back%20in%20the%20States%2C%20the%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20here%20means%20that%20his%20money%20can%20go%20further%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20I%20used%20to%20try%20to%20keep%20my%20budget%20to%20%242%2C000.%20Now%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20than%20that.%20I%20would%20say%20%242%2C500%20is%20what%20I%20live%20on%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20doesn't%20think%20he%20could%20live%20on%20the%20same%20amount%20back%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20a%20basic%20health%20insurance%20policy%20that%20costs%20340%20Malaysian%20ringgit%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20other%20much%20better%20policies%2C%20but%20I%20went%20with%20the%20cheap%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%20He%20says%20it%20only%20covers%20hospitalization%20and%20related%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20satisfied%20with%20Malaysia's%20healthcare%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20wait%20long%20for%20an%20appointment%20or%20wait%20long%20at%20your%20appointment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECost%20of%20living%20aside%2C%20Taylor%20says%20he%20also%20feels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktoker-malaysia-debunking-misconceptions-viral-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafer%20in%20Malaysia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20felt%20safer%20anywhere.%20Where%20I%20lived%20in%20my%20last%20place%20outside%20D.C.%2C%20sometimes%20I%20would%20hear%20gunshots%20from%20outside%20my%20window%2C%20and%20that%20just%20is%20so%20foreign%20here.%20There's%20nothing%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20ever%20felt%20any%20uncomfortable%20feeling%20when%20I'm%20out%2C%20even%20alone%20walking%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20Tayl