it%20to%20Noida%20in%20the%20NCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20all%20night%20packing%20and%20preparing%20the%20shipment%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20collect%20the%20payment.%20The%20vendor%20told%20me%20that%20his%20bank%20account%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20working%20and%20that%20he%20could%20only%20transfer%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20initially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20troubles.%20The%20vendor%20ended%20up%20not%20paying%20the%20remaining%20Rs%204%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20huge%20challenge.%20To%20repay%20the%20loan%2C%20we%20had%20to%20raise%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20from%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20difficulties%20but%20also%20being%20grateful%20for%20the%20support%20he%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201774px)%20100vw%2C%201774px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221774%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20friends%20at%20a%20pop-up%20store%20of%20their%20brand%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437.jpg%201774w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe