aring%20and%20preparing%20the%20land%20for%20farming.%20He%20leased%20a%2012-acre%20plot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20formal%20training%20but%20a%20strong%20willingness%20to%20learn%2C%20Sarbeswar%20began%20farming%20with%20traditional%20methods.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20what%20I%20saw%20other%20elders%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20growing%20eggplant%2C%20chilli%2C%20Assam%20lemon%2C%20and%20other%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20recalls.%20However%2C%20the%20methods%20proved%20insufficient%2C%20and%20the%20land%20lacked%20the%20fertility%20needed%20to%20sustain%20a%20profitable%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitial%20hurdles%20like%20inadequate%20finances%20for%20investment%20into%20agriculture%2C%20lack%20of%20proper%20facilities%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20of%20scientific%20methods%20were%20always%20present.%20Chirang%20was%20a%20backward%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits%2C%20reflecting%20on%20his%20early%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20learnt%20a%20great%20deal%20about%20agriculture%20while%20working%20on%20that%20leased%20land.%20After%20years%20of%20working%20on%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20land%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land%20in%201995.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20learn%20more%2C%20an%20impromptu%20visit%20to%20the%20agriculture%20department%2C%20in%201998%2C%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Sarbeswar.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20began%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20department%2C%20learning%20about%20agriculture%2C%20improving%20yields%2C%20finding%20ways%20to%20increase%20his%20profits%20each%20season%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20intercropping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-sl